<task id="task_378FB18E8C7244CDA8C1D029DBACBAEE">
  <title>Validate Targeting to URL or Referring URL Parameters</title>
  <shortdesc>Follow these steps to validate targeting to a URL or referring URL
	 parameters. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_F9F6CD7DD9204E65997458D64D91D587">
      <step id="step_730A4509EE2147C584FE2497AE75896C">
        <cmd>Append the targeting parameters and values to the end of the URL,
			 or referring page URL. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>The example below shows an appended target condition where your
				targeting condition is met when the keyword equals "chairs": 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <filepath>http://www.yourcompany.com/asp/feature_item.asp?​keyword=chair&amp;categoryId=45</filepath>
          </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_E2719A6E5FC74D7DA26DFAF11D3A1A4D">
        <cmd>Confirm that you see the correct content for the targeting
			 condition. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_9BFA402DC0BA4E5794B3BBC43F8E08DB">
        <cmd>Delete cookies and confirm you do not see the content when you do
			 not meet the targeting condition. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_4456277ED4174497B88496F16FD84E36">
        <cmd>If segments filters are set, confirm reports correctly capture the
			 URL parameter values. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
